   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">To set up the connection to Power (on Salesforce), you must create a Connected App. Install the Connected App in the org you are syncing to enable authentication. After the Connected App is installed, you can get the Client Id and Client Secret required for configuration, as well as user name and password.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Refer to step-by-step instructions on <xref href="https://help.salesforce.com/articleView?id=connected_app_create.htm&amp;type=5"
               format="html"
               scope="external"
               class="- topic/xref ">how to create a Connected App</xref>.</p>
